## AREA 5: Footer Enhancement

### Current State (lines 2774-2783 of JSX, CSS lines 542-549)
A minimal flex row with two `<span>` elements: item count and sync status text ("Syncing..." / "Synced").

### JSX Changes

At lines 2774-2783, update the footer:

```jsx
// BEFORE:
{!isFocusMode && <div className="freedom-wall-footer">
    <span>{sortedItems.length} {isTimeCapsuleMode ? "items in time capsule" : "items this week"}</span>
